summary: The video introduces Brabus, a company founded by a man named Mr. Bushman who customized cars after being told he couldn't drive a Porsche 911 Turbo. He started tuning cars and eventually created Brabus, which combines 'Bra' (Brakman) and 'bus' (Bushman). The video explains the origin of the brand and showcases a red Mercedes-Benz car.
keywords: Brabus, Mercedes-Benz, car, customization, tuning, Porsche, 911 Turbo, s-class, V8 BITURBO, B-R-A, Bushman, Brakman
